query.sfwSql:
SELECT O.ORG_CODE AS ORGCODEID, A.CONTACT_TICKET_ID AS TICKETNUMBER, CV2.DESCRIPTION AS SEMINARTYPE, C.USER_ID AS FACILITATOR, A.SEMINAR_DATE1 AS SEMINARDAY1, A.SEMINAR_DATE2 AS SEMINARDAY2, A.ATTENDEE_FEE AS ATTENDEEFEE, B.SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL_ID AS SEMINARATTENDEEID
FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE A INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL B ON A.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = B.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV2 ON CV2.CODE_ID=A.SEMINAR_TYPE_ID AND CV2.CODE_VALUE=A.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGS_USER C ON A.FACILITATOR=C.USER_SERIAL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_CONTACT_TICKET CT ON CT.CONTACT_TICKET_ID=A.CONTACT_TICKET_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION O ON O.ORG_ID=CT.ORG_ID
WHERE ((@ddlFacilitator <> '' AND A.FACILITATOR=@ddlFacilitator ) OR @ddlFacilitator= '') AND ((@ddlSeminarType <> '' AND A.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE=@ddlSeminarType) OR @ddlSeminarType= '') AND (A.SEMINAR_DATE1 BETWEEN @start_date AND @end_date) AND A.SEMINAR_CANCEL_FLAG<>'Y' AND B.GUEST_SPEAKER_FLAG <> 'Y'
SELECT * FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE = CASE WHEN @IS_NEW_DEF_COMP = 'Y' THEN 'NDFC' ELSE 'DEFC' END AND SEMINAR_DATE1 > GETDATE()

SELECT PER.last_name + ', ' + PER.first_name + ' ' +PER.MIDDLE_NAME AS PERSON_NAME, PER.PERSON_ID AS PersonID, PER.DATE_OF_BIRTH AS DATEOFBIRTH,PLA.PLAN_NAME AS PLANNAME, SCH.SEMINAR_DATE1 AS SEMINARDATE, * FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE SCH WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL DET WITH(NOLOCK) ON SCH.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID=DET.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID lEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PERACC WITH(NOLOCK) ON PERACC.PERSON_ID = DET.PERSON_ID lEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH(NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=DET.PERSON_ID lEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PLAN PLA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PLA.PLAN_ID = PERACC.PLAN_ID WHERE SEMINAR_DATE1 BETWEEN @FROMDATE AND ISNULL(@TODATE,GETDATE()) AND ((@SEMINARTYPE <> '' AND SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE=@SEMINARTYPE) OR @SEMINARTYPE= '') AND ISNULL(DET.ATTENDED_FLAG,'Y')='Y' AND ISNULL(DET.GUEST_SPEAKER_FLAG,'N')='N' AND DET.PERSON_ID IS NOT NULL AND SCH.SEMINAR_CANCEL_FLAG <>'Y' AND PLA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE <> 'INSR' AND PERACC.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE IN ('ENL1','ENL3','SUS1','SUS2')

SELECT A.* FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE A WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('PREN') AND (SEMINAR_DATE1 >= GETDATE() OR SEMINAR_DATE2 >=GETDATE())
UNION
SELECT A.* FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = B.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID AND B.PERSON_ID = @personID WHERE SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('ONSC','PREE') AND (A.SEMINAR_DATE1 >= GETDATE() OR A.SEMINAR_DATE2 >=GETDATE())

Declare @intSeminarValidityDays INT; select @intSeminarValidityDays= cast(DATA1 as int) from SGS_CODE_VALUE where CODE_ID=52 and CODE_VALUE='SPAY'
select distinct a.*,@orgID as org_id , SeminarStatus=(case When DATEADD (day , @intSeminarValidityDays*-1 , a.seminar_date1 ) < GetDate() THEN 'Closed' ELSE 'Open' END) from sgt_seminar_schedule a WITH(NOLOCK) inner join sgt_contact_ticket b on a.contact_ticket_id = b.contact_ticket_id where ((seminar_type_value in ('PAYC','AUTH'))) AND B.STATUS_VALUE = 'OPEN'

-- Def Comp Agents who had training earlier within 2 years SELECT DISTINCT C.*, SS.SEMINAR_DATE1 FROM SGT_CONTACT C WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC WITH(NOLOCK) ON C.CONTACT_ID = OC.CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR WITH(NOLOCK) ON OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN ( SELECT SAD.CONTACT_ID,SS.SEMINAR_DATE1, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY SAD.CONTACT_ID ORDER BY SS.SEMINAR_DATE1 DESC) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL SAD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE SS WITH(NOLOCK) ON SAD.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = SS.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID WHERE SS.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DEFC','NDFC') AND SAD.ATTENDED_FLAG = 'Y' AND --SS.SEMINAR_DATE1 > DATEADD(YEAR,-2,@EFFECTIVEDATE) YEAR(@EFFECTIVE_DATE)-YEAR(SS.SEMINAR_DATE1) = 2 ) SS ON SS.CONTACT_ID=C.CONTACT_ID WHERE OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE = 'AGNT' AND OC.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' AND OC.PLAN_ID IN (8, 19) AND ROWRANK =1 AND ISNULL(C.EXEMPT_FROM_TRAINING_FLAG,'N') <> 'Y' --PROD PIR ID 3243

-- Def Comp Agents who had NO recent training SELECT DISTINCT C.*, SS.SEMINAR_DATE1, ORG.ORG_CODE, ORG.ORG_NAME FROM SGT_CONTACT C WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC WITH(NOLOCK) ON C.CONTACT_ID = OC.CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR WITH(NOLOCK) ON OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON OC.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID INNER JOIN ( SELECT SAD.CONTACT_ID,SS.SEMINAR_DATE1, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY SAD.CONTACT_ID ORDER BY SS.SEMINAR_DATE1 DESC) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL SAD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE SS WITH(NOLOCK) ON SAD.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = SS.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID WHERE SS.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DEFC', 'NDFC') AND SAD.ATTENDED_FLAG = 'Y' ) SS ON SS.CONTACT_ID=C.CONTACT_ID WHERE OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE = 'AGNT' AND OC.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' AND OC.PLAN_ID IN (8, 19) AND ROWRANK=1 AND SS.SEMINAR_DATE1 <= DATEADD(YEAR,-1,@EFFECTIVEDATE) AND ISNULL(C.EXEMPT_FROM_TRAINING_FLAG,'N') <> 'Y' --PROD PIR ID 3243
UNION
-- Def Comp Agents who had NO training at all SELECT DISTINCT C.*, NULL AS 'SEMINAR_DATE1', ORG.ORG_CODE, ORG.ORG_NAME FROM SGT_CONTACT C WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT OC WITH(NOLOCK) ON C.CONTACT_ID = OC.CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE OCR WITH(NOLOCK) ON OC.ORG_CONTACT_ID = OCR.ORG_CONTACT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON OC.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID WHERE OCR.CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE = 'AGNT' AND OC.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' AND OC.PLAN_ID IN (8, 19) AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT DISTINCT 'X' FROM SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL SAD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE SS WITH(NOLOCK) ON SAD.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = SS.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID WHERE SAD.CONTACT_ID = C.CONTACT_ID AND SS.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DEFC', 'NDFC') AND SAD.ATTENDED_FLAG = 'Y' ) AND ISNULL(C.EXEMPT_FROM_TRAINING_FLAG,'N') <> 'Y' --PROD PIR ID 3243
ORDER BY CONTACT_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE WHERE SEMINAR_DATE1 BETWEEN GETDATE() AND DATEADD(DD, 21,GETDATE()) AND SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE IN ('PREE','PREN') AND ISNULL(CONFIRMATION_SENT_FLAG, 'N') <> 'Y'

SELECT SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID,SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL.PERSON_ID ATTENDEE_PERSON_ID, SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.SEMINAR_DATE1, SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.LOCATION_NAME, SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.LOCATION_ADDRESS, SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.LOCATION_CITY, SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.MEETING_ROOM, SGS_CODE_VALUE.DESCRIPTION AS SEMINAR_TYPE_DESCRIPTION FROM SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL INNER JOIN SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE ON SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE ON SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.SEMINAR_TYPE_ID = SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_ID AND SGT_SEMINAR_SCHEDULE.SEMINAR_TYPE_VALUE = SGS_CODE_VALUE.CODE_VALUE WHERE (SGT_SEMINAR_ATTENDEE_DETAIL.SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID = @SEMINAR_SCHEDULE_ID) AND PERSON_ID IS NOT NULL
